		]a
		".
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"When Leon is crouched (like in the part of the war where you can crouch in the bags), if you aim, Leon will stand up. However, if you stand up, aim, enter the briefcase and equip another weapon, Leon will exit the crouching animation, but the game will understand that he is still crouched. By doing this, you can crouch anywhere, just by pressing the aim button. This happens at 13:45 and can only be done on GameCube (as far as I remember). See 
		[a href=https://youtu.be/16FDgDp3_VA rel=noopener external nofollow 
			"here.
