	[li 
		"When equipped with Infinite Rocket Launcher, if you aim with the knife and while aiming, take any attack or damage, Leon will bug and hold the RPG in the middle of his body lol. This is just a graphical glitch, nothing major happens.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"When Leon aims, whether with a knife or a gun, Ashley stays behind him. If you do this near a wall, Ashley ends up going inside the wall. If you do this on the edge of a floor, she loses her collision with the floor. By throwing eggs, you can make her float in the air. This happens at 
